OL,3,CCouncil considering fining residents
OL,4,Cfor leaving out bins
OL,6,FA council is considering imposing
OL,7,Ffines on residents who leave their
OL,8,Fbins on the street once they've been
OL,9,Femptied.
OL,11,FA six-month pilot scheme is being
OL,12,Fproposed for the centre of Tewkesbury
OL,13,Fin Gloucestershire, covering homes in
OL,14,Fthe town's historic conservation area.
OL,16,FTewkesbury Civic Society raised
OL,17,Fconcerns that the bins are spoiling
OL,18,Fthe town centre, devaluing properties
OL,19,Fand making pavements less accessible.
