OL,3,CCouncil considering fining residents
OL,4,Cfor leaving out bins
OL,6,FA working group was set up by the
OL,7,Fborough council to address the issue
OL,8,Fafter it received a petition from
OL,9,FTewkesbury Civic Society.
OL,11,FSociety chair Alan Purkiss said: "Bins
OL,12,Fare left out forever, on both sides of
OL,13,Fthe road. You just see bins, when you
OL,14,Freach the main inlet once you come off
OL,15,Fthe motorway."
OL,17,FITV West Country spoke to a number of
OL,18,FTewkesbury residents about what they
OL,19,Ffelt should be done.
