OL,3,CCouncil considering fining residents
OL,4,Cfor leaving out bins
OL,6,FOne resident said: "There's no where
OL,7,Fto put the bins, yes, it doesn't look
OL,8,Fnice, but there's no alternative, the
OL,9,Fcouncil has to give people something,
OL,10,Fand then if they don't use it, then
OL,11,Ffine them. You can't fine people if
OL,12,Fthere's no where to put the bins."
OL,14,FAnother resident said: "You can't help
OL,15,Fit sometimes, there's no where else to
OL,16,Fleave the bins. What happens if you're
OL,17,Faway? Your neighbours may not be happy
OL,18,Fto do your bins, I think the fines are
OL,19,Fjust a way for the council to make
OL,20,Fmoney."
