OL,3,CCouncil considering fining residents
OL,4,Cfor leaving out bins
OL,6,FOne resident spoke of how most locals
OL,7,Fare elderly and struggle moving bins,
OL,8,F"Most people are not mobile enough to
OL,9,Fmove their bins around."
OL,11,FAnd a man who relies on his mobility
OL,12,Fscooter to get around the village told
OL,13,Fus, the bins left out on the street
OL,14,Fmake it inaccessible: "We can't get
OL,15,Fpast, it causes us to crash and when
OL,16,Fpeople are walking on the pavement it
OL,17,Fcauses jams.
