OL,3,CCouncil considering fining residents
OL,4,Cfor leaving out bins
OL,6,FThe council said it doesn't want to
OL,7,Ffine people, bur rather persuade them
OL,8,Fto take their bins off the pavement.
OL,9,FThey say there is a proposal to work
OL,10,Fwith the community to tackle the
OL,11,Fproblem. And that fines are an option,
OL,12,Fbut not what they are looking to do.
OL,14,FThe councils next move is yet to be
OL,15,Fdecided.
